author: pradine
msg: Changes related to AXIS2-1516. The wsa:To and wsa:ReplyTo headers are now omitted if they contain a wsa anonymous address. This applies to the 2005/08 adressing namespace only. In addition, the RelationshipType attribute is now omitted if the value is wsa reply. This applies to both namespaces.
